  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<ol><li>Assist in execution of Main Contracts administrative documents. Contract administration for client, main contractor, consultants, sub- contractor and suppliers.</li><li>Preparation of Monthly Progress Claims and consolidation of team's supporting documents to see through to client's requirements on claim reviewing.</li><li>Assist the team on quantity take offs, estimation, prepare tender submission, cost planning, sourcing sub-contractors, forecast budgeting, variation orders, final accounts.</li><li>Assistance with recording of meeting minutes and timelines.</li><li>Preparation and Issuance of Contracts to Sub-Contractors and Suppliers</li><li>Preparation for Payment Response to sub- contractor and suppliers</li><li>Suppliers contact and liaising over pricing for comparison, quotation and confirmation of materials.</li><li>Position is based on Project Site location, Full Time.</li><li>Past Experience required. </li></ol>",
